55658.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
55658.description: When SpongeBob and Patrick accidentally destroy Sandy's air supply, they have to help her find more oxygen. // SpongeBob wants to earn his belt from karate master Fuzzy Acorns. Will Sandy be able to help?

55659.title: Avatar: The Last Airbender
55659.description: As one of Aang's little detours, the group heads toward the island of Kyoshi. But soon they learn that the townspeople don't trust foreigners at all; however, when Aang proves to them that he is the Avatar they are treated as guests of honor. Katara wants to get some supplies and leave as soon as possible, while Aang is enjoying his time as a celebrity. Little do they know, though, that the Fire Nation has tracked them down. Also, Sokka meets and trains with a female warrior named Suki. Will Aang be able to save the village from the wrath of the Fire Nation?

55660.title: Avatar: The Last Airbender
55660.description: Aang takes Katara and Sokka back to a favorite place he used to go to when he was younger, the Earth Kingdom City of Omashu. But when they break the law they are taken to the King to get their punishment. The eccentric King of Omashu puts Aang through a series of challenges and if he fails Katara and Sokka will be engulfed in a crystal cocoon

55661.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
55661.description: Mr. Krabs hires Squidward to babysit Pearl for the night, but she just wants to sneak out to a cool teen party! // After spilling a milkshake during a delivery, SpongeBob vows to return and clean the entire building!

55662.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
55662.description: Plankton tells Patrick he's his conscience so he can convince the wooden-headed star to steal him a Krabby Patty. // When Mr. Krabs puts in an open kitchen, SpongeBob gets stage fright and has to invent a new persona.

55663.title: Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles
55663.description: When the Rat King returns, Splinter must overcome his guilt and fear of the Rat King controlling his mind in order to defeat his foe once and for all.

55664.title: Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles
55664.description: Facing Shredder's deadly new assassin, Leo must decide whether to risk his brother's lives or ask for Splinter's help. Donnie must put aside his rivalry with Casey in order to uncover a new Kraang plot.

55665.title: Kung Fu Panda: Legends of Awesomeness
55665.description: When a rhino comes to the Valley of Peace seeking to destroy the Dragon Warrior, Po tries to befriend him before he discovers Po's true identity.

55666.title: Kung Fu Panda: Legends of Awesomeness
55666.description: After Po unleashes an 'impossible move', he's told that the most powerful fighter in the Valley of Peace always turns evil, and that's him!

55667.title: The Penguins of Madagascar
55667.description: The penguins discover the abuse that Randy the sheep gets in the children's zoo from all the children with sticky hands tugging at his wool, and decide to find him a new home. // The duckling Eggy is back. The training that the penguins gave him worked.

55668.title: The Penguins of Madagascar
55668.description: The penguins are on a mission to fulfill wishes. Private tells Mort that if he throws a penny in the fountain his wish will come true. // King Julien has just discovered April Fools Day. Making up for lost time, he terrorizes the zoo with pranks.

55669.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
55669.description: When The Krusty Krab runs out of mustard, Mr. Krabs sends SpongeBob, Patrick and Squidward to dig up some more! // SpongeBob and Sandy have to collect Krabby Patty ingredients, but Plankton is following their every step.

55670.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
55670.description: Mr. Krabs hires Squidward to babysit Pearl for the night, but she just wants to sneak out to a cool teen party! // After spilling a milkshake during a delivery, SpongeBob vows to return and clean the entire building!

55671.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
55671.description: Plankton tells Patrick he's his conscience so he can convince the wooden-headed star to steal him a Krabby Patty. // When Mr. Krabs puts in an open kitchen, SpongeBob gets stage fright and has to invent a new persona.

55672.title: Nella The Princess Knight
55672.description: Nella goes on a quest for Bling Berries in the Murkberry Mines so she can make her mom's favorite pancakes for breakfast! // Nella and Blaine must find three baby dragons when they go missing from a play-date.

55673.title: Nella The Princess Knight
55673.description: When Nella's sword gets an amazing upgrade she finds it difficult to master its new power. // It's the Castlehaven Jousting Tournament and all the gang want to win!

55674.title: Bubble Guppies
55674.description: Blast off with the Bubble Guppies - it's time to learn all about the solar system! Help them begin to learn about outer space in this far-out episode.

55675.title: Bubble Guppies
55675.description: Pack a suitcase and hurry to the airport! Help the Bubble Guppies fly an airplane through the sky and over the clouds - just be sure to keep an eye out for airplane pirates!

55676.title: Dora the Explorer
55676.description: Meet Rojo, the newest, shiniest red fire truck. Rojo invites our heroes along as he goes on his very first rescue mission - to help a kitten who's stuck in a tree.

55677.title: Dora the Explorer
55677.description: Who do we ask for help when we don't know which way to go? The Map! But today the Map gets mistaken for a stick by a goofy bird. The bird flies Map all the way to his nest on top of Tallest Mountain.

55678.title: Rusty Rivets
55678.description: When the mischievous monkeys escape from their Animal Park enclosure, Rusty must find a way to lead them back. // When the town's power goes out after Ruby takes Crush up for a fun plane flight, there's no light on the ground to help them land.

55679.title: Rusty Rivets
55679.description: When Crush wanders off and gets lost, Rusty invents a night flyer to find him in the dark. // When Liam loses his stuffy out the train window, Rusty goes on a retrieval mission using a mechanical spider suit to climb up under the trestle and drop down like a spider to get it.

55680.title: Blaze And The Monster Machines
55680.description: Blaze and his friends have joined the Truck Rangers, a scouting club where trucks earn badges for their accomplishments. But when Crusher's selfish scouting lands everyone in a heap of trouble, Blaze must race to the rescue!

55681.title: Blaze And The Monster Machines
55681.description: When an overeager Crusher causes the Truck Wash to explode out into Axle City, Blaze and friends will need your help using angles to recover the pieces and get the trucks clean again!

55682.title: PAW Patrol
55682.description: The pups' road trip through the savanna becomes a mission to reunite and rescue an elephant family! // To win the Spotless Town award, the PAW Patrol pups must save Adventure Bay from Mayer Humdinger's Kitten Catastrophe Crew!

55683.title: PAW Patrol
55683.description: When Marshall decides to take a break from the PAW Patrol, the pups jump into action to bring him back! // When the pups find a stowaway on their trip to the Icy Tundra, they must rescue a run-away kitty on a run-away Snow Cat!

55684.title: PAW Patrol
55684.description: Mayor Goodway calls on the Paw Patrol to rescue her twin niece and nephew from a tree, and then twin sit for the day! // Expecting the fireworks for Adventure Bay Day, Mayor Goodway receives a package of piglets after a mix-up!

55685.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
55685.description: SpongeBob and Patrick try to join the extreme sports team The Drasticals. // Sandy finds a book of world’s records, and tries to break them all with SpongeBob’s help.

55686.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
55686.description: SpongeBob learns his milkshake license has expired, and is forced to go back to the milkshake academy. // Squidward hits his head and reverts to being a baby, and it's up to SpongeBob and Patrick to take care of him.

55687.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
55687.description: Squidward finds SpongeBob's diary, and starts reading it out loud in the Krusty Krab. // SpongeBob once again fails his driving test, forcing Mrs. Puff to think outside the box--and off the road.

55688.title: The Penguins of Madagascar
55688.description: It's off to the races when Skipper agrees to give a day off from hard training to the first penguin who can bring him a kipper. Private, Rico, and Kowalski battle their way to a fish packing plant where they discover Officer X has become Fishmonger X. The deranged X sniffs out the fighting penguins, capturing them and hauling them off to the pokey. Can they rediscover the teamwork they had forsaken in order to escape? High Moltage: The penguins are determined to make opening day of their favorite action star's blockbuster movie! Private, however, has an itchy problem - he's turned hideous because he's molting! The penguins need his hypercute powers to knock Alice out and disengage her new zoo security system. The despondent bird does all he can to reconstruct his cuteness, but sadly his hypercute powers distort to cause a hyperalarming, hypervomitous mess!

55689.title: The Penguins of Madagascar
55689.description: The Penguins are faced with a global battle when their specialty food-making machine belches out a toxic cloud that threatens not just the zoo, not just the city, but the earth itself!

55690.title: Kung Fu Panda: Legends of Awesomeness
55690.description: After Po unleashes an 'impossible move', he's told that the most powerful fighter in the Valley of Peace always turns evil, and that's him!

55691.title: Kung Fu Panda: Legends of Awesomeness
55691.description: After Po disobeys Shifu's orders, the Hierarchy of the Sacred Onyx Council replaces Shifu with a new master who banishes the Furious Five and plans to destroy Shifu.

55692.title: Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles
55692.description: The Turtles return to the city to search for Splinter, only to find that the city is overrun with Kraang.

55693.title: Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles
55693.description: As the Turtles search for Karai, they have to deal with a city filled with Kraangdroids as well as Zeck and Steranko, who hunt Karai for their own means.

55694.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
55694.description: Everyone is in awe of Larry the Lobster's daredevil ways, especially SpongeBob and Patrick. // Everybody who's anybody is going to a big party in Bikini Bottom, but you have to be a certain shade of tan to get in.

55695.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
55695.description: When Squidward gets spritzed with plant growth spray, he becomes monstrously huge. // When Patrick realizes that he is the only one out of all his friends without a nose, he decides he needs to get a nose, too.

55696.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
55696.description: It's time to restock the secret Krabby Patty ingredient, and it is SpongeBob's duty to make sure the ingredient is delivered safely to the Krusty Krab. // Plankton has a customer who eats at the Chum Bucket every day.

55697.title: Kung Fu Panda: Legends of Awesomeness
55697.description: After Po disobeys Shifu's orders, the Hierarchy of the Sacred Onyx Council replaces Shifu with a new master who banishes the Furious Five and plans to destroy Shifu.

55698.title: Kung Fu Panda: Legends of Awesomeness
55698.description: When Mantis returns to his hometown claiming to be the Dragon Warrior to impress his ex-fiancé, Po pretends to be his sidekick who doesn't know kung fu.

55699.title: The Penguins of Madagascar
55699.description: The toy manufacturer of Rico's doll-girlfriend has upgraded their doll line with a voice chip. // When the penguins are photographed while in action and placed on the new zoo poster they have to stop the presses before the poster gets out to the public.

55700.title: The Penguins of Madagascar
55700.description: King Julien observes children chasing each other, calling out "cooties". He deduces that girls pass this wretched "cooties" with a simple touch. // When Rico crashes the Penguins car and rebuilds it himself, it becomes "possessed" and targets Rico.

55701.title: Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles
55701.description: Facing Shredder's deadly new assassin, Leo must decide whether to risk his brother's lives or ask for Splinter's help. Donnie must put aside his rivalry with Casey in order to uncover a new Kraang plot.

55702.title: Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles
55702.description: The Turtles try to relax by playing a fantasy role-playing game, but when the game becomes real, they must learn the difference between fantasy and reality.

55703.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
55703.description: The Krabby Patty That Ate Bikini Bottom: Mr Krabs uses Sandy’s experimental growth formula on a Krabby Patty with disastrous results. Bubble Buddy Returns: SpongeBob tries to keep Bubble Buddy’s visiting son, Shiny, out of trouble and away from sharp edges.

55704.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
55704.description: Restraining SpongeBob (fka Whispering Tentacles): Annoyed by SpongeBob for the last time, Squidward issues him a restraining order. Fiasco! (fka The Priceless Patty): Plankton steals a Krabby Patty from the Krusty Krab, unaware it’s really an art piece by famous artist Fiasco.

55705.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
55705.description: After Plankton drives away Mr. Krabs' customers, Mr. Krabs is forced to give out free Krabby Patties to try to win them back. // SpongeBob's pineapple is falling apart, and he needs all of his friends to help him remodel it!

55706.title: Kung Fu Panda: Legends of Awesomeness
55706.description: Shifu tells the citizens of the Valley of Peace that whoever can defeat Po before sunset will become the new Dragon Warrior. When Hundun hears of the challenge, he returns to the village to claim the title.

55707.title: Kung Fu Panda: Legends of Awesomeness
55707.description: After Po gets trapped in a hole, Fung helps him out and is owed a favor. Will it be a costly one?

55708.title: The Penguins of Madagascar
55708.description: The Amarillo Kid confronts the penguins looking for the infamous Mr. Tux. Apparently the two have a score to settle. // Private is ready to move up in rank within the penguin commando unit, or is he? First he'll have to become a First Class Private.

55709.title: The Penguins of Madagascar
55709.description: Kowalski is near completion with his mind reading device. But where can he find a processor? // The zoo's new badger exhibit has Private terrified. Marlene sets out to calm his panic by introducing him to the new zoo neighbors, Becky and Stacy.

55710.title: Avatar: The Last Airbender
55710.description: When the group arrives at a small Earth Kingdom mining town, they see an earthbender, named Haru, who is practicing his ability, but he runs away when Katara tries to confront him about it. They soon learn that the Fire Nation has taken over the town, that earthbending is forbidden and all earthbenders are taken away to an offshore prison. However, when an elderly man is trapped in a collapsed mine, Katara urges Haru to use his powers to save the man's life, but then, the old man reports Haru to the authorities. Katara blames herself for his predicament and she vows to rescue him, but will she succeed?

55711.title: Avatar: The Last Airbender
55711.description: When Aang is assigned to help defend a town from a monster that has been plaguing the town, his lack of ability and knowledge becomes obvious, as he doesn't know what to do. However, when Sokka tries to rush to Aang's rescue during the fight, he himself becomes captured and is taken away by the monster, which turns out to be from the spirit world. Aang promises Katara that he'll find Sokka and bring him back, but with Aang even doubting himself, will he be capable of finding where the monster went?

55712.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
55712.description: Karen 2.0 (fka Computer Trouble): Plankton’s computer wife Karen ends up working at the Krusty Krab after being replaced by the newer, better Karen 2. InSPONGEiac: SpongeBob can’t get to sleep, and asks for help from Patrick—who thinks he can’t stay awake.

55713.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
55713.description: SpongeBob and Patrick make a bet to see who can hold a "funny face" the longest...then their faces freeze that way! // SpongeBob and Patrick spend one last glorious - and dangerous - day at Glove World before it closes for good.

55714.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
55714.description: SpongeBob brings home a box of new snail treats that Gary will do anything to get - especially when they run out. // Plankton wins a free Krabby Patty, and Mr. Krabs will do anything to stop him from collecting.

55715.title: Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles
55715.description: Feeling guilty for turning April's father into a mutant bat, the Turtles perfect a retro-mutagen to help him. Unfortunately, things get worse when Baxter Stockman threatens to mutate April.

55716.title: Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles
55716.description: Raph is worried about Casey's ability to handle big mutant threats...when they meet Slash again and discover he has a partner of his own: THE NEWTRALIZER!

55717.title: Kung Fu Panda: Legends of Awesomeness
55717.description: To impress his fan club, Po releases the Mongolian Fist Demon. Now he has to figure out how to defeat the Demon and save the village and his fans!

55718.title: Kung Fu Panda: Legends of Awesomeness
55718.description: Po disobeys Shifu's orders and looks into the Mystical Mirror of Yin and Yang, creating two versions of himself: one good and one evil!

55719.title: The Penguins of Madagascar
55719.description: Due to the high rate of gadget malfunction, Skipper orders Kowalski to cease with the science. But Kowalski can't resist, he must invent. // When a baby's stroller rolls outside the zoo the penguins chase the baby through the streets of New York.

55720.title: The Penguins of Madagascar
55720.description: The penguin's habitat must undergo a serious repair. So Alice calls in Gus, a strong willed contractor. The penguins must stop Gus before he unearths their secret HQ. // When King Julien wishes on the Gimme Gimme Star, he gets more than he asked for.

55721.title: The Penguins of Madagascar
55721.description: Julien suspects a plot to overthrow or kill him is being orchestrated by Maurice. // Burt discovers a love for painting. He's very talented. Kowalski's blueprints for a quantum accelerator get mixed in with his paintings and end up in the museum.

55722.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
55722.description: Plankton teams up with Man Ray to take over the Krusty Krab and then-the world! Hahahahahaha! // Squidward quits the Krusty Krab to work for Plankton, turning the Chum Bucket into an overnight success.

55723.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
55723.description: The Good Krabby Name: Mr. Krabs wants all of Bikini Bottom to eat at the Krusty Krab, so SpongeBob and Patrick go on an advertising blitz. Move It or Lose It: Mr. Krabs and Plankton circulate petitions to see which restaurant will get bulldozed by the city.
